{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Reference (参照)","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Glossary/Reference","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web\"></a><a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/Object\">オブジェクト</a>の文脈において&nbsp;<a href=\"/js/docs/Web\"></a><a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/Object_reference\">オブジェクト参照</a>を指します。MDNでは <a href=\"/js/docs/Web\"></a><a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/JavaScript\">JavaScript</a>&nbsp;参照自体を指す場合があります。</p>\n\n<p>コンピューティングにおいては、参照は間接的にアクセスし、コンピューターメモリやその他ストレージデバイスの変数やレコードを取得する値を指します。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"詳細情報","title":"詳細情報","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"一般知識","title":"一般知識","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Wikipedia記事 <a title=\"参照 (情報工学)\" href=\"https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/参照_(情報工学)\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">参照 (情報工学)</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"詳細情報","id":"詳細情報"}],"summary":"オブジェクトの文脈において オブジェクト参照を指します。MDNでは JavaScript 参照自体を指す場合があります。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Reference","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Référence","locale":"fr","native":"Français"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/glossary/reference","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/glossary/reference/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Glossary","title":"MDN Web Docs 用語集: ウェブ関連用語の定義"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Glossary/Reference","title":"Reference (参照)"}],"pageTitle":"Reference (参照) - MDN Web Docs 用語集: ウェブ関連用語の定義 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}